[#reference_optional_constructor]

[: `optional<T>::optional();`]

* [*Effect:] Default-Constructs an `optional`.
* [*Postconditions:] `*this` is [_uninitialized].
* [*Throws:] Nothing.
* Notes: T's default constructor [_is not] called.
* [*Example:]
``
optional<T> def ;
assert ( !def ) ;
``

