[: `template<U> optional& optional<T` ['(not a ref)]`>::operator= ( optional<U> const& rhs ) ;`]

* [*Effect:] Assigns another convertible optional to an optional.
* [*Postconditions:] If `rhs` is initialized, `*this` is initialized and
